  "title": "API proposal : let the user pass a reference to a file for templating",
  "body": "In order to make templating very easy and well done, we could provide a way to load the template from a URL. The code could look like : \n\n``` js\nvar template = InstantSearch.templateLoader;\n\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.hits({\n    container: '#hits',\n    templates: {\n      empty: 'No results',\n      hit: template('./templates/hit.html')\n    },\n    hitsPerPage: 6\n}));\n```\n",
